      "title": "Robot Tax UBI Calculator",
      "content": "Robot Tax CalculatorDisplacement Dividend Forecaster\nRobot Tax 1-3.7% funds UBI for 491 daily job losses. Enter your state to see your monthly Displacement Dividend projection.\nUBI Eligibility Calculator\nThe Robot Tax Revolution: 2026 Policy Landscape\nGlobal robotics market projected to generate $4.7 trillion in economic value. A 2.1% tax rate would fund $98.7 billion in annual UBI payments for displaced workers.\nWorld Economic Forum projects 85 million jobs displaced by automation. At current subprime rates, displaced workers lose an additional $714 billion in excess interest.\n5 states have active robot tax bills. 12 more have study committees. Federal ROBOT Act proposes national 2.1% rate with UBI distribution formula.\nThe UBI Trap: Why Displacement Dividends Aren't Enough\nNET BENEFIT: $144/yr ($12/mo). UBI barely covers subprime penalties.\nFix credit to 740+ first = keep 100% of your displacement dividend."
